, I had a new joy and hope for life. I managed to leave behind the pain and suffering that had been thrust upon me. I could experience the joy and happiness of other people. I relaxed for 5 ♥♥♥♥ minutes listening to this music, long enough to realize that I would be okay.After realizing this, I turned off the game and went back to work. My hand hurt a lot, but I was motivated. I stopped feeling so sorry for myself and became the father I needed to be at that moment, not the weak boy I was behaving like.Today, I am close friends with the mother of my children. We don\'t fight, argue, or say hurtful things to each other. We are parents and friends.Now I have 3 children. My third child is, wait, ALSO 4 YEARS OLD. The woman I am with was going through a very similar situation at the time of my separation, and we just unexpectedly stumbled into each other\'s lives. We have been dating for a year and are very happy together.Moral of the story: you never know what life has in store for you, and if I had given up when all odds were against me, I wouldn\'t be where I am today. This silly little game helped me realize that.Thank you.',''),(2209,'Locked at 40-48 FPS, even after having a High End Laptop specification and above the recommended requirements. I\'m mentioning the FPS at game\'s lowest settings, not playable :(:(',''),(2210,'WHY DO I STILL HAVE TO BUY EXTRA CAR PACKS EVEN THO I BOUGHT THE PREMIUM VERSION100 BUCKS',''),(2211,'i drive',''),(2212,'This is a very good game that has it all. Very much to do and if you like tuning, upgrade parts and styling too, you will love it probably .I had to sell my PC to buy a real car IRL, but hopefully I will get money so I can buy a PC again to play this more.',''),(2213,'Listen, forza saved my life. (i like drifting in this game and have a wheel) but anyways i was at a light when it was raining and i gunned it a little too hard so my car spun out and started going sideways. so i did what i know best and started countersteering l